This looks good to me.  An incredibly minor nit pick is included (sorry).

This also brings up the issue of testing caching.  Other bugs have come up that only occur when an image is downloaded twice (to trip caching).  It would be good to automate our existing functional tests that download to run twice, once with a single download and again with a 2 downloads.
